'''Laire Squadron''' was a group of [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]] belonging to the [[Mugaari]]. They participated in the [[Defense of Outpost D-34|First Battle of Javin]] against the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Space station/Legends|platform]] known as [[Outpost D-34]]. They were destroyed in the battle.

==Behind the scenes==
''[[TIE Fighter: The Official Strategy Guide]]'' erroneously classifies starfighters from Laire Squadron as [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|''Z-95 Headhunters'']].

